<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('partials/head', { pageTitle: 'About Us' }) %>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <section class="container section narrow">
    <h1 class="section-title">About <%= siteInfo.name %></h1>
    <p>
      <%= siteInfo.name %> was founded in <%= siteInfo.founded %> to make buying and
      selling used vehicles simple, transparent and trustworthy. Whether you are
      looking for a reliable second-hand car, a bike for your daily commute, or a
      scooter for quick city rides, we connect buyers directly with verified sellers.
    </p>
    <p>
      This particular build is a classroom assignment demonstrating a Node.js and
      Express application with server-rendered EJS views. All listings, sellers and
      testimonials are hardcoded in <code>data/listings.js</code> — there is no
      database, and no data is persisted between requests.
    </p>
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      To provide a straightforward, no-nonsense marketplace where every listing is
      accurate and every seller is accountable.
    </p>
  </section>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
